+**Data model (canonical, v2+):**
+- `lib/types/index.ts` — TypeScript types for `Character`, `Build`, `EquippedItem`, `RolledAffix`, `AppliedAspect`, `SkillSelection`, `ParagonAllocation`, `PlaystyleConstraint`, and all catalog types. This is the single source of truth; the scoring engine (v3+) and API import (v3) consume these types.
 
